palette = ['#1e6f5c','#f2b84b','#e76f51','#3a86ff','#8338ec','#2a9d8f','#264653','#ff7b00','#6d597a','#43aa8b','#577590','#bc4749']

def esc_xml(s):
    return (str(s).replace('&','&amp;').replace('<','&lt;').replace('>','&gt;').replace('"','&quot;'))

def wrap_text(text, max_len=17, lines=3):
    words = text.split()
    out=[]; cur=''
    for w in words:
        if len(cur)+len(w)+1 <= max_len:
            cur = (cur+' '+w).strip()
        else:
            out.append(cur); cur=w
            if len(out) >= lines-1: break
    if cur and len(out) < lines: out.append(cur)
    return out[:lines]

shape_width = {'widebody':160,'traditional':145,'hybrid':150,'elongated':130}
def shape_key(shape):
    s=shape.lower()
    if 'widebody' in s: return 'widebody'
    if 'traditional' in s: return 'traditional'
    if 'hybrid' in s: return 'hybrid'
    return 'elongated'

def make_paddle_svg(p, idx):
    c1 = palette[idx % len(palette)]
    c2 = palette[(idx+3) % len(palette)]
    key = shape_key(p['shape'])
    w = shape_width[key]
    x = 200 - w/2
    rx = {'widebody':36,'traditional':42,'hybrid':40,'elongated':48}[key]
    body_h = {'widebody':220,'traditional':230,'hybrid':235,'elongated':255}[key]
    body_y = 58
    handle_y = body_y + body_h - 6
    handle_h = 128
    model_lines = wrap_text(p['model'], 18, 3)
    model_text = ''.join([f'<text x="200" y="{170+i*26}" class="model">{esc_xml(line)}</text>' for i,line in enumerate(model_lines)])
    traits = ' · '.join(p.get('traits', [])[:3]).upper()
    price = f"${p['priceUsd']:.2f}" if p.get('priceUsd') else p.get('priceBand','')
    return f'''<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="720" height="900" viewBox="0 0 400 500" role="img" aria-labelledby="title desc">
<title id="title">{esc_xml(p['brand'])} {esc_xml(p['model'])} illustrated paddle card</title>
<desc id="desc">A stylized non-photographic product card created for PickleLevel.</desc>
<defs>
  <linearGradient id="g" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1"><stop offset="0" stop-color="{c1}"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="{c2}"/></linearGradient>
  <radialGradient id="spot" cx="50%" cy="38%" r="65%"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#fff" stop-opacity=".22"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#000" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient>
  <filter id="shadow" x="-20%" y="-20%" width="140%" height="140%"><feDropShadow dx="0" dy="14" stdDeviation="13" flood-color="#14231f" flood-opacity=".22"/></filter>
  <style>
    .brand{{font:700 20px Arial,sans-serif;letter-spacing:.12em;fill:#ffffff;text-anchor:middle}}
    .model{{font:800 22px Arial,sans-serif;fill:#ffffff;text-anchor:middle}}
    .small{{font:700 11px Arial,sans-serif;letter-spacing:.10em;fill:#e8fff8;text-anchor:middle;opacity:.9}}
    .price{{font:900 25px Arial,sans-serif;fill:#1b2a26;text-anchor:middle}}
  </style>
</defs>
<rect width="400" height="500" rx="28" fill="#f6fbf7"/>
<rect x="20" y="20" width="360" height="460" rx="24" fill="#ffffff" stroke="#d9e8df"/>
<g filter="url(#shadow)">
  <rect x="{x:.1f}" y="{body_y}" width="{w}" height="{body_h}" rx="{rx}" fill="url(#g)"/>
  <rect x="{x:.1f}" y="{body_y}" width="{w}" height="{body_h}" rx="{rx}" fill="url(#spot)"/>
  <path d="M{200-w/2+18:.1f} {body_y+32} C {200-w/2+50:.1f} {body_y+8}, {200+w/2-50:.1f} {body_y+8}, {200+w/2-18:.1f} {body_y+32}" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-opacity=".35" stroke-width="3"/>
  <rect x="174" y="{handle_y}" width="52" height="{handle_h}" rx="20" fill="#2c2f31"/>
  <rect x="179" y="{handle_y+9}" width="42" height="{handle_h-18}" rx="17" fill="#3d4448"/>
  <path d="M183 {handle_y+22} h34 M183 {handle_y+44} h34 M183 {handle_y+66} h34 M183 {handle_y+88} h34" stroke="#eaf4f1" stroke-opacity=".28" stroke-width="3"/>
</g>
<text x="200" y="112" class="brand">{esc_xml(p['brand'].upper())}</text>
{model_text}
<text x="200" y="262" class="small">{esc_xml(p['style'].replace('-', ' ').upper())} · {esc_xml(shape_key(p['shape']).upper())}</text>
<rect x="105" y="405" width="190" height="48" rx="24" fill="#f2b84b"/>
<text x="200" y="437" class="price">{esc_xml(price)}</text>
<text x="200" y="382" class="small" fill="#1e6f5c">{esc_xml(traits)}</text>
</svg>'''

for idx,p in enumerate(paddles):
    (paddle_dir/f"{p['slug']}.svg").write_text(make_paddle_svg(p, idx), encoding='utf-8')

